    <pre>Conclusion: If there were a landing page for "I want to start helping a 
project", then we could introduce people to the concept of bitesize bugs.

Discussion from #openhatch:

&lt;poisonarms&gt; well i thought itd be a good idea to sort the problems by 
ease, some of us with what could probably be described with less than 
junior developer status, such as myself, may have trouble wondering 
where to start
&lt;paulproteus&gt; poisonarms: Yeah, I see what you mean.
&lt;paulproteus&gt; Have you tried the "bite-size" bug listing?
&lt;paulproteus&gt; I will say that it's not entirely consistent; some projects' 
"easy" bugs are still quite hard for a newcomer.
&lt;poisonarms&gt; i have not, i was stumbling and came to a blog about the 
website</pre>
